et elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e878a96\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Hypertension<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Elevated Blood Pressure<\/em>: SBP \u2265 120 mmHg (DBP &lt; 80 mmHg)<\/li><li><em>Hypertension, Stage 1 (Mild)<\/em>: \u2265 130\/80 mmHg<\/li><li><em>Hypertension, Stage 2 (Moderate)<\/em>: \u2265 140\/90 mmHg<\/li><li><em>Hypertensive Crisis (Severe)<\/em>: \u2265 180\/120 mmHg<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Causes<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Essential Hypertension<\/em>: Hypertension without Any Identifiable Cause<\/li><li><em>Secondary Hypertension<\/em>: Hypertension Due to an Identifiable Cause<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Severe Hypertension<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Hypertensive Urgency<\/em>: Severe Hypertension without Signs of End-Organ Damage<\/li><li><em>Hypertensive Emergency<\/em>: Severe Hypertension with Signs of End-Organ Damage<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Complications of Hypertension<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Cardiac Sequelae:<ul><li>Heart Failure<\/li><li>Acute Coronary Syndrome\/Myocardial Infarction (MI)<\/li><li>Left Ventricular Hypertrophy<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Neurologic Sequelae:<ul><li>Ischemic Stroke<\/li><li>Intracerebral Hemorrhage<\/li><li>Hypertensive Encephalopathy<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Vascular\/Renal Sequelae:<ul><li>Aortic Dissection<\/li><li>Acute Kidney Injury<\/li><li>Chronic Kidney Disease<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ebe662d elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ebe662d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-01a427b\" data-id=\"01a427b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a671c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a671c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Evaluation<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4154636 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4154636\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-93661ba\" data-id=\"93661ba\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83e39d8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"83e39d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Vitals<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>ABC\u2019s \u2013 Airway, Breathing &amp; Circulation<\/li><li>Vital Signs<\/li><li>Repeat Blood Pressure Reading to Ensure Accuracy<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Signs of Hypertensive Emergency<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Chest Pain<\/li><li>Back Pain<\/li><li>Dyspnea<\/li><li>Altered Mental Status<\/li><li>Seizures<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Evaluate Potential Causes of Secondary Hypertension<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Inadequate Pain Control<\/li><li>Anxiety<\/li><li>Bladder Distention<\/li><li>Acute Volume Repletion<\/li><li>Hypothermia<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5fb86c4 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5fb86c4\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fcbf15c\" data-id=\"fcbf15c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-825fe9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"825fe9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Inpatient Treatment<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-844aaa7 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"844aaa7\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-658eccd\" data-id=\"658eccd\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2fae843 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2fae843\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Inpatient Blood Pressure Goal<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>General Inpatient Goals:<ul><li>SBP &lt; 160 mmHg<\/li><li>DBP &lt; 100 mmHg<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Pitfalls:<ul><li>Inpatient Goals are Poorly Defined with <strong>Minimal Evidence to Support Treating Isolated, Episodic Asymptomatic Hypertension<\/strong><\/li><li>Some Patients May Require Stricter Blood Pressure Goals \u2013 Large Epidural Hematomas, Carotid Endarterectomy (CEA), etc.<\/li><li>Outpatient Goals are Generally Lower<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Initial Managements<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Aggressively Manage for Any Signs of Hypertensive Emergency \u2013 Symptomatic or Signs of End-Organ Damage<\/li><li>Treat Any Possible Secondary Causes \u2013 Pain, etc.<\/li><li>Restart Any Previously Held Home Antihypertensive Medications<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>General Approach<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Generally Start with PRN IV Medications<ul><li>Common Starting Medications: Hydralazine or Labetalol<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>May Require Antihypertensive Drip (gtt) for Urgent and Precise Control<\/li><li>Consider Adding a Long-Acting Oral Medication if Continuing to Require Frequent IV Dosing<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b621974 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"b621974\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c88b5df\" data-id=\"c88b5df\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f8d1000 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f8d1000\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Antihypertensive Medications<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-200f29